The,Office,of,Energy,Efficiency,and,Renewable,Energy,of,the,United,States,Department,of,Energy,provides,this,API,to,help,rate,commercial,buildings,on,energy,efficiency,according,to,its,national,standards,Using,a,variety,of,physical,characteristics,and,likely,usage,the,tool,can,rate,a,building,s,energy,efficiency,including,evaluating,its,systems,and,identifying,areas,for,possible,upgrades